install Django 
: python language behind Django 

start :
virtualenv name
cd name
source bin/activate
pip install django==version
pip freeze // confirm it !
django-admin.py startproject start // compatibility issue between python and django versions 

Django version	Python versions
1.11	          2.7, 3.4, 3.5, 3.6, 3.7 (added in 1.11.17)
2.0	            3.4, 3.5, 3.6, 3.7
2.1, 2.2	      3.5, 3.6, 3.7

cd start 
 start->|_manage.py
        |_start
        
 and start has it dudeeeee!!!!!!! (so excited )
 |-> __init__.py
 |-> settings.py
 |-> urls.py
 |-> wsgi.py (web server gateway interface)
 
 cd ..
 
 the root of the project is always where manage.py is !
  
